# Project Velocity Dashboard

> Track project activity, identify stale projects, and monitor development momentum.

---

## Quick Stats

```dataviewjs
const projects = dv.pages('"Projects"').where(p => p.type === "project");
const now = Date.now();
const day = 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000;

const fresh = projects.filter(p => (now - p.file.mtime) < 7 * day).length;
const stale = projects.filter(p => (now - p.file.mtime) >= 7 * day && (now - p.file.mtime) < 14 * day).length;
const rotting = projects.filter(p => (now - p.file.mtime) >= 14 * day).length;

dv.paragraph(`🟢 **Fresh (<7d):** ${fresh} | 🟡 **Stale (7-14d):** ${stale} | 🔴 **Rotting (>14d):** ${rotting}`);
```

