## Project Freshness

Projects sorted by time since last update. Green is healthy, yellow needs attention, red is critical.

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link as "Project",
  status as "Status",
  priority as "Priority",
  round((date(today) - file.mtime).days) as "Days Since Update",
  choice((date(today) - file.mtime).days < 7, "🟢 Fresh",
    choice((date(today) - file.mtime).days < 14, "🟡 Stale", "🔴 Rotting")) as "Health"
FROM "Projects"
WHERE type = "project"
SORT (date(today) - file.mtime).days ASC
```

