## Tech Stack Coverage

Technologies used across active projects:

```dataviewjs
const projects = dv.pages('"Projects"').where(p => p.type === "project");
const techMap = new Map();

projects.forEach(p => {
  const stack = p["tech-stack"] || [];
  stack.forEach(tech => {
    // Clean up the tech string (remove wiki-link formatting)
    let name = String(tech);
    name = name.replace(/\[\[.*?\|/g, '').replace(/\]\]/g, '').replace(/\[\[/g, '');
    techMap.set(name, (techMap.get(name) || 0) + 1);
  });
});

if (techMap.size > 0) {
  const sorted = [...techMap.entries()].sort((a, b) => b[1] - a[1]);
  dv.table(["Technology", "Used In Projects"], sorted);
} else {
  dv.paragraph("*No tech stacks defined in project frontmatter*");
}
```

