## Attention Required

Projects that need immediate attention (high priority + stale):

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link as "Project",
  priority as "Priority",
  status as "Status",
  round((date(today) - file.mtime).days) as "Days Stale"
FROM "Projects"
WHERE type = "project"
  AND (priority = "P0" OR priority = "P1")
  AND (date(today) - file.mtime).days > 7
SORT priority ASC
```

